01-qljb/26cul-maids-off-broadway-01-qljb-videoSixteenByNineJumbo1600.jpg" medium="image"><media:credit>Richard Termine for The New York Times</media:credit><media:description>Power dynamic: Saban and Ha in Kip Williams’s production, which was rewritten in a contemporary idiom while hewing closely to Genet’s plot.</media:description></media:content></item><item><title>Five Ways A.I. Search Beats an Old-School Google Search</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/technology/personaltech/google-ai-mode-search.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/technology/personaltech/google-ai-mode-search.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</guid><atom:link rel="standout" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/07/technology/personaltech/google-ai-mode-search.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss" /><description>Google’s A.I. search technology is far from perfect (don’t count on it for celebrity news), but it excels at tasks like picking out groceries and detecting scams.</description><dc:creator>Brian X. Chen</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 09:03:06 GMT</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Artificial intelligence</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Search Engines</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Computers and the Internet</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Tech Industry</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Fraud</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">E Commerce</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Travel</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Tourism</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">vacations</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/n